     <script>
      function addAltImage() {
            $("img").each(function(){
                var alt = $(this).attr("alt");
                if(alt==null||alt==''){
                    var src = $(this).attr("src");
                    var altValue ='';
                    var srcRen = '';
                    if (src) {
                      if(src.indexOf('/_jcr_content/renditions/cq5dam')!=-1){
                          srcRen = src.substring(0,src.indexOf("."));
                          altValue = srcRen.substring(srcRen.lastIndexOf("/")+1);
                      }else{
                          altValue = src.substring(src.lastIndexOf("/")+1, src.lastIndexOf("."));
                      }
                    }

                     altValue = altValue.replace(/-/g, ' ').replace(/_/g, ' ');

                    $(this).attr("alt",altValue);
                }else{
                        alt = alt.replace(/-/g, ' ').replace(/_/g, ' ');
                        $(this).attr("alt",alt);
                   }
            });
        }

        function updateMySmartCouponsInfo() {
            var totalValuefromCat = 0;
            var category = $.ajax({
                type: "GET",
                url: 'https://www.familydollar.com/bin/familydollar/servlets/inmarCategoryServlet',
                dataType: "json",
                
                success: function(filterData){
                    totalValuefromCat = filterData.totalValue[0];
                    $(".savingsSc").html("Available: $" + totalValuefromCat);
                }
            });
            
            if(loginedUser !== undefined && loginedUser.inmarData !== undefined){
              $(".clippedCountSc").html(loginedUser.inmarData.clippedSummary.clippedCount);
              $(".clippedValueSc").html("My Wallet: $" + formatCurrency(loginedUser.inmarData.clippedSummary.clippedValue));
            }

            if(window.Intl) {
                 var formatter = new Intl.NumberFormat('en-US', { style: 'currency', currency: 'USD', minimumFractionDigits: 2 });
             }
        }

        $( document ).ready(function () {
            addAltImage();
            var cID = getCookie('cID');
            var token = getCookie('token');
            var inmarToken = getCookie('inmarToken');

            $("#registration").show();
            $("#stickyRegistration").show();
            if (cID != null && cID !== '' && token != null && token !== '' && inmarToken != null && inmarToken !== '') {
                $.ajax({
                    type: 'POST',
                    url:'https://www.familydollar.com/bin/familydollar/servlets/users',
                    data:"operation=4" + '&resourcePath=https://www.familydollar.com/content/familydollar/en/sitemap/jcr:content' + '&cID=' + cID + '&token=' + token + '&inmarToken=' + inmarToken,
                    success: function(json) {
                        loginedUser = json;
                        $(".firstname").text('Hi, ' + loginedUser.firstName);
                        $(".fullname").text('Hi, ' + loginedUser.firstName + ' ' + loginedUser.lastName);

                        //hide help menu item
                        $("#helpMenu").hide();

                        $('.loggedin').show();
                        $('.loggedin-mobile').show();

                        // Update Sc Info
                        updateMySmartCouponsInfo(loginedUser);

                        //$('.not-loggedin').removeClass('not-loggedin').addClass('loggedin');
                       
                         $(document).trigger('userData', loginedUser);
                        $(document).trigger('logined');
                    },
                    error: function (xhr, ajaxOptions, thrownError) {
                        console.log('Error to checking user login');
                        $('.not-loggedin').show();
                        $(document).trigger('not-logined');
                    },
                    complete: function(jqXHR, textStatus) {
                    }
                });
            } else {
                $('.not-loggedin').show();
                $(document).trigger('not-logined');
            }
        });
        $(document).on('click', '#logoutBtn', function() {
            console.log('Logout');
            setCookie('user-token','');
            if(localStorage.getItem("jStorage")!=null){
                localStorage.removeItem("jStorage");
            }
            window.location.href= $(this).attr('href');
        });

         (function(){
          var setStoreLocator = {

             init: function(loginedUser) {
                this.userinfo = loginedUser;

                this.getStoreInfo(loginedUser);
                this.fillStoreToCookie(loginedUser);
                this.neighborStore(loginedUser);
                this.eventHandler();
              },

              eventHandler : function(){
                var self = this;
        
                 $(document).on('click', '.makeMyStore', function(e){
                    e.preventDefault();
                     if($(e.target).attr('data-storeinfo')){
                        var data = $(e.target).data('storeinfo');
                           if(self.userinfo !== 'undefined'){
                              self.userinfo.store = data;
                              self.putStoreInfo(data);
                              self.fillStoreToCookie(data);
                            }
                     }
                })
              },
        
              getStoreInfo: function(data) {
                this.setStoreInfo(data);
              },

              setStoreInfo : function(data){
                  if(data !== undefined && data.store !== undefined){
                   var street = data.store.streetAddress[0],
                        city = data.store.city,
                        state = data.store.state,
                        phone = data.store.phone,
                        address = street + ", " + city + ", " + state,
                        accountAddress = street + "<br>" + city + ", " + state + "<br>"+ phone;

                   $('#topbaraddress').html(address);
                  
                   if($('.store-right').length > 0){
                      $('.store-right').find('span').html(accountAddress);
                   }
                  }
              },

              putStoreInfo: function(store) {

                var userinfo = setStoreLocator.userinfo,
                    self = this;

                  if(store !== 'undefined'){
                    // ----------Post store data -----------//
                    $.ajax({
                        type: 'POST',
                        url: 'https://www.familydollar.com/bin/familydollar/servlets/users',
                        data: 'editType=store' + '&' + 'store=' + JSON.stringify(store)
                        + '&' + 'operation=2' + '&' + 'cID=' + userinfo.cID + '&' 
                        + 'inmarToken=' + userinfo.inmarToken + '&' + 'token=' + userinfo.token
                        + '&' + 'resourcePath=https://www.familydollar.com/content/familydollar/en/sitemap/jcr:content',
                        error: function(xhr) {
                        //console.log(xhr)
                          // var errorResp = jQuery.parseJSON(xhr.responseText);
                        },
                        success: function(json) {
    
                            self.setStoreInfo(json)
                        }
                      });
                    }
        
                },

                fillStoreToCookie : function (objectStore) {
                  if(objectStore !== undefined && objectStore.store !== undefined){

                    var stringTemp = '',
                      wallChar = ':::',
                      brChar = '<br />',
                      space = ' ',
                      dot = ',',
                      address = '',
                      sAddress = objectStore.store.streetAddress,
                      hours = '',
                      sHours = objectStore.store.hours,
                      includeTopBarAddress = '';

                    stringTemp += objectStore.store.id + wallChar;

                    for (var i = 0; i < sAddress.length; i++) {
                      if (sAddress[i] && sAddress[i].length) {
                        address += sAddress[i] + brChar;
                      }
                    };

                    includeTopBarAddress += address.replace(/<br \/>/g, "") + dot + space;
                    includeTopBarAddress += objectStore.store.city + dot + space;
                    includeTopBarAddress += objectStore.store.state + space;
                    includeTopBarAddress += objectStore.zipCode;

                    stringTemp += address;
                    stringTemp += objectStore.store.city + '|' + space;
                    stringTemp += objectStore.store.state + space;
                    if (objectStore.store.zipCode) stringTemp += objectStore.store.zipCode + wallChar;
                    if (objectStore.store.phone) stringTemp += objectStore.store.phone + wallChar;

                    if(sHours !== undefined && sHours.length){
                    for (var j = 0; j < sHours.length; j++) {
                        for (var j = 0; j < sHours.length; j++) {
                            if (sHours[i] && sHours[i].length) {
                                hours += sHours[j] + brChar;
                            }
                        }
                    }
                    };
                    stringTemp += hours + wallChar;
                    stringTemp += Math.round(objectStore.store.distance);

                    setCookie('mystoreinfo', stringTemp);
                    setCookie('mystore', objectStore.store.id);
                  }
                },

                neighborStore : function(data){
                  if(data !== undefined && data.store !== undefined){
                    var output = "";
                    var sHours = "";
                    if(data.store.hours !== undefined){
                        var sHours = "<p class='hours'> "+data.store.hours.join('<br>');
                    }


                    output+= "<div class='distance'>Neighborhood store <span>"+ Math.round(data.store.distance) +" mi</span></div><div id='myStore'>"
                              +"<div class='store'><div class='storeInfo'><div class='name'><strong>Family Dollar #"+data.store.id+"</strong></div>"
                              +"<div class='address'>"+data.store.streetAddress[0]+",<br>"+data.store.city +", "+data.store.state+"</div><span class='phone'>"+data.store.phone+"</span><div class='moreInfo'>"+sHours+"</p>"
                              +"<a class='weeklyAds' href='https://www.familydollar.com/weekly-ads?drpStoreID="+data.store.storeNumber+"'>Weekly Ads</a> |"
                              +"<a class='coupons' href='https://www.familydollar.com/smartcoupons'>Coupons</a> |"
                              +"<a class='directions externalLink' target='_blank' href='https://maps.google.com?daddr="+encodeURIComponent(data.store.streetAddress[0]+data.store.city+data.store.state)+"' title='link opens in new window'>Directions</a>"
                              +"</div></div></div></div>";


                     $('#currentStore').html(output);
                     $('#currentStore').show();
                   }
               }
            }

         $(document).on('userData', function(e, data){
              setStoreLocator.init(data);
        });

    })();
     </script>

    function handleAutosuggestSearch() {
        var searchText = encodeURIComponent($("#sli_search_2_wi2200059").val().trim()) + "*";
        var searchTextDisplay = '"' + $("#sli_search_2_wi2200059").val() + '"';
        return $.ajax({
            url: domain + "/ccstoreui/v1/search?Ntt=" + searchText
        }).then(function(data) {
            if (data && data.resultsList && data.resultsList.records && data.resultsList.records.length > 1) {
                $('#autosuggest_desktop_container').css('display', 'block');
                $('#autosuggest_desktop_search_term').text(searchTextDisplay);
                var productsElement = $('#autosuggest_desktop_products');
                productsElement.empty();
                productsElement.append('<ul>');
                for (var i = 0; i < data.resultsList.records.length; ++i) {
                    var record = data.resultsList.records[i];
                    if (record.records && record.records[0] && record.records[0].attributes) {
                        var displayName = record.records[0].attributes["product.displayName"][0];
                        var link = record.records[0].attributes["product.route"][0];
                        var image = record.records[0].attributes["product.primaryThumbImageURL"][0];
                        productsElement.append('<li class="product" style="list-style-type: none;"><a href=' + link + '><div class="row"><div class="col-sm-2"><div class="product-thumb" style="background-image:url(' + image + ')"></div></div><div class="col-sm-6"><div class="product-name">' + displayName + '</div></div></div></a></li>');
                    }
                }
                productsElement.append('</ul>');
            } else {
                $('#autosuggest_desktop_container').css('display', 'none');
            }
        });
    }

    function handleSearchRedirect(id) {

    (function () {
        /*!
            * JavaScript Cookie v2.2.0
            * https://github.com/js-cookie/js-cookie
            *
            * Copyright 2006, 2015 Klaus Hartl & Fagner Brack
            * Released under the MIT license
            */
        (function (factory) {
            var OldCookies = window.Cookies;
            var api = window.Cookies = factory();
            api.noConflict = function () {
                window.Cookies = OldCookies;
                return api;
            };
        }(function () {
            function extend() {
                var i = 0;
                var result = {};
                for (; i < arguments.length; i++) {
                    var attributes = arguments[i];
                    for (var key in attributes) {
                        result[key] = attributes[key];
                    }
                }
                return result;
            }
            function decode(s) {
                return s.replace(/(%[0-9A-Z]{2})+/g, decodeURIComponent);
            }
            function init(converter) {
                function api() {
                }
                function set(key, value, attributes) {
                    if (typeof document === 'undefined') {
                        return;
                    }
                    attributes = extend({
                        path: '/'
                    }, api.defaults, attributes);
                    if (typeof attributes.expires === 'number') {
                        attributes.expires = new Date(new Date() * 1 + attributes.expires * 864e+5);
                    }
                    // We're using "expires" because "max-age" is not supported by IE
                    attributes.expires = attributes.expires ? attributes.expires.toUTCString() : '';
                    try {
                        var result = JSON.stringify(value);
                        if (/^[\{\[]/.test(result)) {
                            value = result;
                        }
                    } catch (e) {
                    }
                    value = converter.write ?
                        converter.write(value, key) :
                        encodeURIComponent(String(value))
                            .replace(/%(23|24|26|2B|3A|3C|3E|3D|2F|3F|40|5B|5D|5E|60|7B|7D|7C)/g, decodeURIComponent);
                    key = encodeURIComponent(String(key))
                        .replace(/%(23|24|26|2B|5E|60|7C)/g, decodeURIComponent)
                        .replace(/[\(\)]/g, escape);
                    var stringifiedAttributes = '';
                    for (var attributeName in attributes) {
                        if (!attributes[attributeName]) {
                            continue;
                        }
                        stringifiedAttributes += '; ' + attributeName;
                        if (attributes[attributeName] === true) {
                            continue;
                        }
                        // Considers RFC 6265 section 5.2:
                        // ...
                        // 3.  If the remaining unparsed-attributes contains a %x3B (";")
                        //     character:
                        // Consume the characters of the unparsed-attributes up to,
                        // not including, the first %x3B (";") character.
                        // ...
                        stringifiedAttributes += '=' + attributes[attributeName].split(';')[0];
                    }
                    return (document.cookie = key + '=' + value + stringifiedAttributes);
                }
                function get(key, json) {
                    if (typeof document === 'undefined') {
                        return;
                    }
                    var jar = {};
                    // To prevent the for loop in the first place assign an empty array
                    // in case there are no cookies at all.
                    var cookies = document.cookie ? document.cookie.split('; ') : [];
                    var i = 0;
                    for (; i < cookies.length; i++) {
                        var parts = cookies[i].split('=');
                        var cookie = parts.slice(1).join('=');
                        if (!json && cookie.charAt(0) === '"') {
                            cookie = cookie.slice(1, -1);
                        }
                        try {
                            var name = decode(parts[0]);
                            cookie = (converter.read || converter)(cookie, name) ||
                                decode(cookie);
                            if (json) {
                                try {
                                    cookie = JSON.parse(cookie);
                                } catch (e) {
                                }
                            }
                            jar[name] = cookie;
                            if (key === name) {
                                break;
                            }
                        } catch (e) {
                        }
                    }
                    return key ? jar[key] : jar;
                }
                api.set = set;
                api.get = function (key) {
                    return get(key, false /* read as raw */);
                };
                api.getJSON = function (key) {
                    return get(key, true /* read as json */);
                };
                api.remove = function (key, attributes) {
                    set(key, '', extend(attributes, {
                        expires: -1
                    }));
                };
                api.defaults = {};
                api.withConverter = init;
                return api;
            }
            return init(function () {
            });
        }));
    })();
    function adjustFullSizeContainersWidth() {
        var $fullWidthContainers = $('.full-width'),
            clientWidth = document.documentElement.clientWidth;
        $fullWidthContainers.css({
            'width': clientWidth + 'px',
            //'margin-left': (-clientWidth / 2) + 'px'
        });
        $fullWidthContainers.each(function (index, item) {
            item.style.setProperty('margin-left', (-clientWidth / 2) + 'px', 'important');
            item.style.setProperty('left', '50%', 'important');
        })
    }
    function handleMenu() {
        $('.dropdown-submenu').on('mouseover', function () {
            $('.dropdown-menu-visible').removeClass('dropdown-menu-visible');
            $(this).children('.sbd-submenu-dropdown').addClass('dropdown-menu-visible');
        });
        $(".dropdown").hover(function () {
            setTimeout(function () {
                var container = $("#sbd-menu-dropdown");
                var offset = 0;
                var height = container.outerHeight();
                $(container).find(".sbd-submenu-dropdown").each(function (index, item) {
                    $(item).css("height", height).css("top", -offset);
                    offset += $(item).closest(".dropdown-submenu").outerHeight();
                });
            });
        });
    }
    function handleStickyHeader() {
        var self = {
            isVerticallyScrolled: ko.observable(false),
            instanceName: ko.observable(''),
            isPreview: ko.observable(false)
        };
        self.isVerticallyScrolled.subscribe(function (val) {
            $('.occ-static-composite-header-widget-fd .header-inner').toggleClass(
                'fixed-header', val);
            adjustFullSizeContainersWidth();
        });
        $(window).on('scroll', function () {
            var documentScrollTop = $(window).scrollTop(),
                $el = $('.occ-static-composite-header-widget-fd');
            if ($el.length && $el.is(':visible')) {
                //if (!self.openedMenuElement()) {
                if (self.instanceName() !== 'VSC Header' && self.instanceName() !==
                    'DT - Minimal Header') {
                    var $stickyAnchor = $('.header-inner>.row:nth-child(3)', $el),
                        offsetTop = $stickyAnchor.offset().top - (self.isPreview() ? 46 : 0),
                        stickyHeight = $stickyAnchor.data('stickyHeight'),
                        isVerticallyScrolled = documentScrollTop >= offsetTop && (!stickyHeight ||
                            stickyHeight < documentScrollTop);
                    if (self.isVerticallyScrolled() !== isVerticallyScrolled) {
                        $el.height(isVerticallyScrolled ? $el.outerHeight() + 'px' : 'auto');
                        $stickyAnchor.data('stickyHeight', offsetTop);
                        self.isVerticallyScrolled(isVerticallyScrolled);
                    }
                }
                //}
            }
        });
    }
    function handleMobileStickyHeader() {
        var self = {
            isVerticallyScrolled: ko.observable(false),
            isVCS: ko.observable(false)
        };
        self.isVerticallyScrolled.subscribe(function (val) {
            $('.occ-static-composite-header-mobile-widget .header-inner').toggleClass(
                'fixed-header', val);
            adjustFullSizeContainersWidth();
        });
        $(window).on('scroll', function () {
            var documentScrollTop = $(window).scrollTop(),
                $el = $('.occ-static-composite-header-mobile-widget'),
                $headerInner = $('.header-inner>.row:nth-child(1)', $el),
                staticHeaderClass = self.isVCS() ? "static-header-padding-vsc-mobile" :
                    "static-header-padding";
            if ($el && $el.length && $headerInner.height() > 0) {
                if (documentScrollTop < $headerInner.outerHeight()) {
                    self.isVerticallyScrolled(false);
                    $('#main').removeClass(staticHeaderClass);
                } else if (documentScrollTop >= $headerInner.outerHeight()) {
                    self.isVerticallyScrolled(true);
                    $('#main').addClass(staticHeaderClass);
                } else {
                    self.isVerticallyScrolled(false);
                    $('#main').removeClass(staticHeaderClass);
                }
            }
        });
    }

    function handleShipToStore(isECommDisabled) {
        var storeTitle = isECommDisabled ? "Your store: " : "FREE Shipping to Your Store: ";
        var $storeContainer = $('.store-locator-container .links-wrapper:nth-child(2) > span:nth-of-type(2)');
        var $mobileStoreContainer = $('.header-inner .free-shipping-bottom > .store-label');
        adapterWindow.occ.helpers.getShipToStore().then(function (storeLocation) {
            if (storeLocation && storeLocation.code === '1') {
                var address = storeLocation.address2;
                $storeContainer.prev().text(storeTitle);
                $storeContainer.text(address || "");
                $mobileStoreContainer.text(address ? (storeTitle + address) : "");
            }
        });
        // Display (edit) link near the store
        $('.edit-ship-to-store').parent().show(); // Desktop
        $('.free-shipping-bottom > a[href="//www.familydollar.com/store-locator"]').show(); // Mobile
    }
    function handleSignInSectionText() {
        var $userNameSection = $('#CC-loginHeader-myAccount > span:nth-child(2)');
        var $signInSection = $('.user-account-navigation-container');
        var userName = adapterWindow.occ.globalConfig.user().firstName();
        var isLoggedIn = adapterWindow.occ.globalConfig.user().loggedIn();
        if (isLoggedIn) {
            $userNameSection.text(userName);
            $signInSection.show();
            $signInSection.next().hide();
        } else {
            $userNameSection.text('');
            $signInSection.hide();
            $signInSection.next().show();
        }
    }

            '/smart-coupons'));
    }
    function handleFooterButtons() {
        var isUserLoggedIn = adapterWindow.occ.globalConfig.user().loggedIn();
        var $subscribeButton = $('.footer-email-store-section > .left-section-item:first-child button');
        var $storeLocatorButton = $(
            '.footer-email-store-section > .left-section-item:nth-child(2) button');
        $subscribeButton.on('click', function () {
            window.location = isUserLoggedIn ? '/email-preferences' : '/email-subscription'
        })
        $storeLocatorButton.on('click', function () {
            var storeLocatorSearchValue = $('.email-container input').val();
            localStorage.setItem('storeSearchQuery', storeLocatorSearchValue);
            window.location = '/store-locator';
        })
    }

    };

    function xml2json(xml) {
        // Create the return object
        var obj = {};
        if (xml.nodeType == 1) { // element
            // do attributes
            if (xml.attributes.length > 0) {
                obj["@attributes"] = {};
                for (var j = 0; j < xml.attributes.length; j++) {
                    var attribute = xml.attributes.item(j);
                    obj["@attributes"][attribute.nodeName] = attribute.nodeValue;
                }
            }
        } else if (xml.nodeType == 3) { // text
            obj = xml.nodeValue;
        }
        // do children
        if (xml.hasChildNodes()) {
            for (var i = 0; i < xml.childNodes.length; i++) {
                var item = xml.childNodes.item(i);
                var nodeName = item.nodeName;
                if (typeof (obj[nodeName]) == "undefined") {
                    obj[nodeName] = xml2json(item);
                } else {
                    if (typeof (obj[nodeName].push) == "undefined") {
                        var old = obj[nodeName];
                        obj[nodeName] = [];
                        obj[nodeName].push(old);
                    }
                    obj[nodeName].push(xml2json(item));
                }
            }
        }
        return obj;
    }
    function handleSliSearch() {
        var desktop = $('#sli_search_2_wi2200059'),
            mobile = $('#sli_search_1_wi2000036');
        if ($(window).width() < 992) {
            desktop.removeAttr("name");
            mobile.attr("name", "w");
        } else {
            mobile.removeAttr("name");
            desktop.attr("name", "w");
        }
    }
    function handleECommerceStatus(isECommDisabled) {
        function handleDisabledEcomm() {
            $('.shop-by-business').hide();
            $('.dropdown.shop-by-department > a:first-of-type > span:first-of-type').text('Our Departments');
            $('#above-elements').next().find('.category-link-wrapper.top-category.from-catalog > a').text('Our Departments');
            $('#target-shop-by-department > .panel:first-of-type > .category-link-wrapper:first-of-type > a').hide();
            $('#above-elements > .links-wrapper-above:nth-of-type(3)').hide();
            $('.store-locator-container').next().hide();
            $('.store-locator-container img[src=\'/file/general/FD-icon-freeship.png\']').hide()
            $('.links-wrapper.track-order-element-wrapper').hide();
            $('.minicart-element-wrapper').hide();
            $('.occ-cart-mobile-element').hide();
            $('.header-inner > .row:first-of-type > .oc-panel > .login-orders-container').css({'margin-right': '0'});
            $('#links-3 > div:nth-of-type(1)').hide();
            $('#links-3 > div:nth-of-type(2)').hide();
            $('.occ-static-composite-header-mobile-widget > .header-inner > .row:first-of-type').hide();
        }
        if (isECommDisabled) {
            handleDisabledEcomm();
        }
    }
